    "description": "《破灭》是一款别具一格的暗黑风幻想平台动作游戏，手绘画风和动画秀美怡人。玩家需要操控两名截然不同的角色，竭尽全力逃出人称“微笑群岛”的诅咒之地。<br><br>                                 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438480/extras/6de88ae17c70494d6c89b11357743d58.poster.avif?t=1760471563\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438480/extras/6de88ae17c70494d6c89b11357743d58.webm?t=1760471563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >个被诅咒的世界，正等待您去探索</h2>沉浸在强剧情推动的平台战斗中，与全手绘动画展现的独特敌人和多名角色交战并互动。在令人心旌摇曳却又挥之不去的配乐陪伴下，探索神秘又华美的诅咒之境。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438480/extras/47f8eda561f65a78fe3a50852dd72ddc.avif?t=1760471563\" width=630 height=128 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438480/extras/54890efbd4501acc9bb2a47864642d67.avif?t=1760471563\" width=630 height=128 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438480/extras/59cf3651a6ebb1707e899d75a6a7741f.avif?t=1760471563\" width=630 height=128 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438480/extras/f2c4a15ad0642bdcc9a5317a55230189.avif?t=1760471563\" width=630 height=128 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >两名角色供您操控游玩</h2>在两名截然不同的角色之间切换自如，动态体验其独特技能并迎难而上。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438480/extras/e5c3bab1728590d6c2296ac716e99d65.poster.avif?t=1760471563\" width=630 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438480/extras/e5c3bab1728590d6c2296ac716e99d65.webm?t=1760471563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438480/extras/e5c3bab1728590d6c2296ac716e99d65.mp4?t=1760471563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >天渊之子</h2>帮助这个既脆弱又狂野不羁的孩子一路探索、解决谜题，您必须在危机四伏的古老遗迹内披荆斩棘，方能揭开群岛的秘密。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438480/extras/f2f3d25633b7e40b9dec224bafad6145.poster.avif?t=1760471563\" width=630 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438480/extras/f2f3d25633b7e40b9dec224bafad6145.webm?t=1760471563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438480/extras/f2f3d25633b7e40b9dec224bafad6145.mp4?t=1760471563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >救主</h2>这位崇尚暴力的蒙面化身，其天职就是保护孩子们不受救主之地上那些怪诞群魔和邪恶头目的侵害。您必须经历一场又一场快节奏的高强度战斗，神挡杀神、佛挡杀佛，直至冲出微笑群岛。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438480/extras/e336496edc7eeec0d96a2f0dcc37563a.poster.avif?t=1760471563\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438480/extras/e336496edc7eeec0d96a2f0dcc37563a.webm?t=1760471563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438480/extras/e336496edc7eeec0d96a2f0dcc37563a.mp4?t=1760471563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
